    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Food No Drink</strong>, a game where you step into the shoes of a <strong>devious</strong> <strong>student</strong> on a mission to fulfil your hunger. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/e1843aea178be81be3dc15109f86e8d5.poster.avif?t=1744018563\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/e1843aea178be81be3dc15109f86e8d5.webm?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/e1843aea178be81be3dc15109f86e8d5.mp4?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can earn snacks or drinks as <strong>rewards</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/0f8f231db48974f2f39a35c1964c107c.poster.avif?t=1744018563\" width=380 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/0f8f231db48974f2f39a35c1964c107c.webm?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/0f8f231db48974f2f39a35c1964c107c.mp4?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your tools to avoid detection. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/43e75f8f606fb873fa1c5b30452887e9.poster.avif?t=1744018563\" width=380 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/43e75f8f606fb873fa1c5b30452887e9.webm?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/43e75f8f606fb873fa1c5b30452887e9.mp4?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on various tasks from your fellow students, from finding lost items to solving tricky puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/82c07a3101d9a732d8852328bc4a6a54.poster.avif?t=1744018563\" width=422 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/82c07a3101d9a732d8852328bc4a6a54.webm?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192600/extras/82c07a3101d9a732d8852328bc4a6a54.mp4?t=1744018563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Earn Rewards:</strong> Collect a variety of snacks and drinks as rewards for your hard work. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Stealth Mode:</strong> Enjoy your treats without getting caught by the librarian. Use your tools to avoid detection. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Abilities:</strong> Use your earned points to purchase abilities from the shop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maps:</strong> The librarian’s patrol pattern &amp; security level change each map.</p></li></ul>",
